videoDetails.shortDescription:
#AliZafar #PaharonKiQasam #TributeToAliSadpara

Now available on all streaming platforms:
http://bit.ly/PaharonKiQasamTribute-AliZafar

No nation can thrive without recognising and celebrating their heroes. Ali Sadpara was one such unsung hero who dedicated his entire life and risked it to accomplish unprecedented feats for his country. This is the least I could do: sing for an unsung hero so that he is etched into our memories for as long as there is music.

Muhammad Ali Sadpara is the only Pakistani to have climbed eight of the world's 14 highest mountains, and he made the first ever winter ascent of the world's ninth highest peak, Nanga Parbat. Notable achievements of Ali Sadpara are: Gasherbrum II in 2006, Nanga Parbat four time (2008, 2009, 2016 - First winter ascent - and 2017), GI in 2010, Broad Peak Fore summit in 2012, Broad Peak in 2017, K2 in 2018, and Lhotse Makalu and Manaslu in 2019.

Muhammad Ali Sadpara, John Snorri from Iceland and Jp Mohr Prieto from Chile, went missing on February 5 during the expedition to K2.

ALI ZAFAR [OFFICIAL YOUTUBE CHANNEL]
----------------------------------------
He came, he saw and he conquered. Since his first single Channo Ali Zafar has been ruling the hearts of listeners and audiences through his voice, his songs and now his movies. His exceptional and unprecedented achievements has made him an inspiration for million across the globe. Join this page to keep yourself to connect directly with one of the brightest stars of our era!

Ali Zafar is a renowned singer/song writer, actor, painter, music producer, poet and a philanthropist. With 3 Music Albums & 5 Bollywood films to his name!
